snippet.textDisplay: There’s a lot of bright coloring and lighting in this music video. Considering the fact that this song is actually about depression. I feel like Clown is trying to mess with our mind. Thinking this is hype, but it’s actually not. The wavy effects I think are supposed to resemble tears. When you have tears in your eyes, your eyes see differently. The person in the latex trying to escape resembles depression. It feels like you can’t escape it.
